biography:

_About — in the speaker's own words_

I have finished PhD in particle physics in 2019 at CERN and DESY. It was fun to search for new fundamental particles with advanced ML techniques. 
Since 2020, I have been enjoying supporting customers with BlueYonder ML solutions, developing internal tools for forecast evaluation and onboarding new data scientists.
